This paper is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) category as it focuses on studying users' behavior and search queries on mobile devices. The Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category is also likely as the paper discusses collecting mobile query logs. The Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) category is a possibility as the paper mentions collecting user activity and interaction data. The Cybersecurity (cs.CY) category is a less likely possibility as the paper does not mention any security-related aspects. The Other Computer Science (cs.OH) category is also a possibility as the paper discusses designing an Android app and providing a tool to monitor participants and their data.
